OL,11,G0005F999: On the Front Line
OL,12,     GParamedics treat a man with a
OL,13,     Gfast heart rate and chest pains,
OL,14,     Ga woman who has fallen over on
OL,15,     Gher broken shoulder, and a man
OL,16,     Gwith an irregular heartbeat.
OL,17,G0110F24 Hours in A&E
OL,18,     GAlyce, who's 89, is brought to
